# Simulation run output directories (each can be many GB/TB — never commit).
# Covers the DEGRACE/fiducial campaign families plus any box-spec run dir
# (e.g. F5_L512Np2048Ng4096/) regardless of gravity-model prefix.
DEGRACE_*/
fid_*/
LCDM_*/
*Np[0-9]*Ng[0-9]*/
